title: Antihero Deluxe Edition v1.0.4
description:
RUN A THIEVES' GUILD IN A GAS-LIT VICTORIAN UNDERWORLD.

Antihero is a fast-paced digital board game with an (Oliver) Twist. Recruit street urchins, hire thugs, start a gang, upgrade your guild, steal everything... and bribe, blackmail, and assassinate your way to victory. Includes a story-driven campaign, AI skirmishes, and intense online and offline PvP. ONE GOAL. MANY FOES.  Play through the story-driven campaign, skirmish against the AI, and jump online in casual and ranked PvP multiplayer
